summary: Completed comprehensive testing of DentiCompare dental clinic comparison app. Backend APIs are fully functional (21/21 tests passed). Frontend has critical search page bug preventing proper functionality, but other pages work correctly.

ui_bugs.issue: React key duplication warnings for treatment cards
